name: Rimba swing Bali

review 1: An ok attraction to visit, had a joyful ride in an open top (topless) Willy Jeep visiting honey farms and local temples. Our driver has potential pro-photography experience taking cinematic shots and all‚Ä¶ Got to interact with the local community during our drive which was really nice
review 2:

name: Sky Swing Bali
address: Jl. Dewi Saraswati No.9, Karang Dalem I, Bongkasa Pertiwi, Kec. Abiansemal, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80352, Indonesia
review 1: Absolutely worth the visit. Such beautiful surroundings and lots to do. You can balloon up 25mtrs you can go on the sky swing. Lots of birds nests for you to take that special pic. You can quad bike they also offer rafting. You can chill by the pool.  You won't be dissapointed.
review 2: If you are looking to have an experience of taking hot air balloons, don't go here.  They no longer offer hot air balloons.  But they offer other activities like driving around in vw, swing etc.
review 3: Best place to enjoy restaurant food,  extreem swing, take a picture , bird nest, paddyfield and many more.........
review 5: We tried two of the swings and it was great. Especially the one at the left (single swing). The employees did a great job making me feel I am flying! Great experience if you have additional pocket money. Also tried the juices there, which were delicious.
